<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Privacy Policy</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #687d8f 0%, #778b9c 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        nav {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
        }
        nav ul {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            gap: 2rem;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        nav a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: opacity 0.3s;
        }
        nav a:hover {
            opacity: 0.8;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 4rem auto;
            padding: 2rem;
        }
        .content-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 3rem;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #697e90;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        .last-updated {
            color: #999;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            font-style: italic;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #697e90;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }
        p {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: #555;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
            <li><a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a></li>
            <li><a href="/future-improvements">Future Improvements</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="content-card">
            <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: October 15, 2024</p>

            <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
            <p>Welcome to Mile Square Sweeping. We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data. This privacy policy will inform you about how we look after your personal data and tell you about your privacy rights.</p>

            <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
            <p>We collect nothing. All data is stored on device. The only time we receive information is when you fill out data for our feedback form.</p>

            <h2>3. Data Retention</h2>
            <p>Afer we process your feedback, we will either respond to you to get clarification or delete it. We don't want your data. We just want less tickets and easier parking.</p>

            <h2>4. Contact Us</h2>
            <p>If you have any questions about this privacy policy or our privacy practices, please contact us through our contact form.</p>

            <h2>5. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
            <p>We may update our privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new privacy policy on this page and updating the "Last Updated" date. But even then, we still won't collect your data. We just want parking to be easier for Hoboken residents.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
